<BaseLayout title="About | Parvez Shaik" description="About Parvez Shaik - Full-Stack Engineer, Mobile Developer, and DevOps Builder">
	<div class="stack gap-20">
		<main class="wrapper about">
			<Hero
				title="About"
				tagline="Thanks for stopping by! Here’s a bit about my journey, background, and what drives me as an engineer."
			>
				<img
					width="1553"
					height="873"
					src="/assets/at-work.jpg"
					alt="Parvez Shaik working on a full-stack project"
				/>
			</Hero>

			<section>
				<h2 class="section-title">Background</h2>
				<div class="content">
					<p>
						I'm <strong>Parvez Shaik</strong>, a full-stack software engineer with 3+ years of experience building modern applications across web, mobile, and cloud platforms. 
						I specialize in developing scalable and secure systems using <strong>React, Node.js, Spring Boot, Kotlin, Swift, Docker</strong>, and <strong>AWS</strong>.
					</p>
					<p>
						I’ve worked on voting platforms, mobile productivity tools, and CI/CD pipelines — always focusing on code quality, clean architecture, and developer experience. 
						Whether it’s building backend APIs, designing frontend interactions, or automating deployments, I enjoy solving real-world problems with well-crafted software.
					</p>
					<p>
						My passion lies in continuous learning and engineering empowerment. I love building internal tools, improving workflows, and contributing to systems that help others build faster and better. 
						Outside of tech, I’m into strength training, clean eating, and the occasional deep dive into AI, cybersecurity, or creative tech hacks.
					</p>
				</div>
			</section>

			<section>
				<h2 class="section-title">Education</h2>
				<div class="content">
					<p><strong>Master of Science in Computer Science</strong> — Northern Arizona University</p>
					<p><strong>Bachelor of Technology in Information Technology</strong> — Prasad V. Potluri Siddhartha Institute of Technology</p>
				</div>
			</section>

			<section>
				<h2 class="section-title">Skills</h2>
				<div class="content">
					<p>
						<strong>Languages:</strong> JavaScript, TypeScript, Python, Java, Kotlin, Swift, SQL<br />
						<strong>Frontend:</strong> React.js, Next.js, Tailwind CSS, HTML5, CSS3<br />
						<strong>Backend:</strong> Node.js, Express.js, Spring Boot, REST APIs<br />
						<strong>Mobile:</strong> Android (Jetpack Kotlin), iOS (SwiftUI), Flutter (Dart)<br />
						<strong>Cloud & DevOps:</strong> AWS, GCP, Docker, Kubernetes, Jenkins, GitHub Actions, Terraform<br />
						<strong>Databases:</strong> PostgreSQL, MySQL, MongoDB, Firebase Firestore<br />
						<strong>Tools:</strong> Git, VSCode, Android Studio, Xcode, Figma, Notion, Jira
					</p>
				</div>
			</section>
		</main>

		<ContactCTA />
	</div>
</BaseLayout>


<style>
	.about {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 3.5rem;
	}

	img {
		margin-top: 1.5rem;
		border-radius: 1.5rem;
		box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
	}

	section {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 0.5rem;
		color: var(--gray-200);
	}

	.section-title {
		grid-column-start: 1;
		font-size: var(--text-xl);
		color: var(--gray-0);
	}

	.content {
		grid-column: 2 / 4;
	}

	.content :global(a) {
		text-decoration: 1px solid underline transparent;
		text-underline-offset: 0.25em;
		transition: text-decoration-color var(--theme-transition);
	}

	.content :global(a:hover),
	.content :global(a:focus) {
		text-decoration-color: currentColor;
	}

	@media (min-width: 50em) {
		.about {
			display: grid;
			grid-template-columns: 1fr 60% 1fr;
		}

		.about > :global(:first-child) {
			grid-column-start: 2;
		}

		section {
			display: contents;
			font-size: var(--text-lg);
		}
	}
</style>
